## OUTSIDE MIRROR GLASS REMOVAL  


1. Put on gloves and safety glasses.  
2. Push the top of the mirror glass (1).  
3. Pull the bottom of the mirror glass to disengage clips and remove the mirror glass holder with the mirror glass from the frame (2).  

